WEBVTT

00:00:29.160 --> 00:00:30.856
Zapravo, bilo je skoro smiješno

00:00:30.880 --> 00:00:33.536
jer sam uvijek mislila
da će osvajanje takve nagrade

00:00:33.560 --> 00:00:36.216
imati nekakav veliki utjecaj
na moj život,

00:00:36.240 --> 00:00:39.000
ali istina je zapravo 
potpuno suprotna.

00:00:39.840 --> 00:00:41.256
Velike noći,

00:00:41.280 --> 00:00:43.376
postignuća --

00:00:43.400 --> 00:00:44.976
blijede.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:48.416
Ali najteže noći u mom životu
su zapele samnom,

00:00:48.440 --> 00:00:50.936
utjecajući na ono tko sam ja

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:52.680
i što radim.

00:00:53.360 --> 00:00:59.560
U 2010., mom trećem sinu, Joelu, 
dijagnosticiran je rijedak i agresivan tumor na mozgu.